author: Kuokka77
description:
"Squirrel Enthusiasm" by Mutetus/Artline Designs^Onslaught, 3rd at Zoo 2024 C64 music compo.
Art "Going Nuts" by The Sarge/Bonzai^Fairlight, 2nd at Syntax 2022 C64 gfx compo.

Made using real C64 audio in SIDFX dual mono config (identical audio for both chips). Brainworx VST effects applied.

Left channel: MOS 6581R4AR 0187 14 Hong Kong HH512134 HC-30
Right channel: MOS 6581R4 3386 S Philippines IH312143 HC-30

These chips are on the "darker" side of filtering.
title: SID music: Mutetus - Squirrel Enthusiasm (SIDFX 6581 dual mono bx_🎧)
